#: ../../source/user_guide/audio_resources.rst:2
#: 9cef9be8dd644e85914519cb0bae3993
msgid "音频资源"
msgstr "Audio Resources"

#: ../../source/user_guide/audio_resources.rst:4
#: 2a8e6c06a9444149a3fd14d270d2088b
msgid "本章讲“音频文件怎样变成可以播放的资源”。"
msgstr "This chapter explains how audio files become playable resources."

#: ../../source/user_guide/audio_resources.rst:6
#: 362b50ddd3d24c858aed8c918077db78
msgid ""
"在 Godot-FmodPlayer 里，常用资源是 :ref:`FmodAudioStream<FmodAudioStream>`。你可以把它理解成 Godot 侧保存音频数据和播放设置的对象。真正播放时，它会在底层创建 :ref:`Sound<glossary-sound>`，再由播放器或系统播放成一次 :ref:`Channel<glossary-channel>`。"
msgstr ""
"In Godot-FmodPlayer, the commonly used resource is :ref:`FmodAudioStream<FmodAudioStream>`. You can think of it as the Godot-side object that stores audio data and playback settings. When it is actually played, it creates a :ref:`Sound<glossary-sound>` under the hood and plays through a :ref:`Channel<glossary-channel>` managed by a player or by the system."

#: ../../source/user_guide/audio_resources.rst:9
#: f734d65dbd4241fb9fd2fde8d4330cd9
msgid "先选加载方式"
msgstr "Choose a Loading Mode First"

#: ../../source/user_guide/audio_resources.rst:11
#: 18828cd650d849f2930916ec9f86a7d0
msgid "最重要的选择只有一个：长音频用 Stream，短音效用 Sample。"
msgstr "There is one main choice: use Stream for long audio, and Sample for short sound effects."

#: ../../source/user_guide/audio_resources.rst:16
#: c68c8fea8a1b44e7a75dfb3923c17469
msgid "声音类型"
msgstr "Sound type"

#: ../../source/user_guide/audio_resources.rst:17
#: 9447bb74ad2b4c65842602b89cd4cc8a
