msgstr "Either can work"

#: ../../source/user_guide/audio_resources.rst:33
#: d3c3e6b64a324981897ef6ac7e612f34
msgid "优先按项目内存和延迟需求决定"
msgstr "Choose based on your project's memory and latency needs."

#: ../../source/user_guide/audio_resources.rst:35
#: ba4efefdf9f94253badba3c675f6dde0
msgid "这两个概念也可以看 :ref:`Stream 与 Sample<glossary-stream-sample>`。"
msgstr "See also :ref:`Stream and Sample<glossary-stream-sample>` for these concepts."

#: ../../source/user_guide/audio_resources.rst:38
#: 100dab922d7a41f98eb0b73301ae6276
msgid "FmodAudioStream"
msgstr "FmodAudioStream"

#: ../../source/user_guide/audio_resources.rst:40
#: 645fbb8f9142458081a293a4e7c58e90
msgid "**FmodAudioStream** 是最常用的音频资源类。它保存音频数据和创建模式，例如是否流式播放、是否作为样本加载、是否循环。"
msgstr ""
"**FmodAudioStream** is the most commonly used audio resource class. It stores audio data and the creation mode, such as whether the sound streams, loads as a sample, or loops."

#: ../../source/user_guide/audio_resources.rst:43
#: 58985cbb1e804dd49badffd4b7e308e8
msgid "常用创建模式"
msgstr "Common Creation Modes"

#: ../../source/user_guide/audio_resources.rst:48
#: 111282d2f2564309b84d0b4bd6ff8992
msgid "标志"
msgstr "Flag"

#: ../../source/user_guide/audio_resources.rst:49
#: f3d74fb8b9ec4b1a9654ab2fe38a29a8
msgid "说明"
msgstr "Description"

#: ../../source/user_guide/audio_resources.rst:51
#: 49ecd11651794aad845af5b4b984801e
msgid "流式播放，适合音乐和长音频"
msgstr "Streams audio, suitable for music and long audio."

#: ../../source/user_guide/audio_resources.rst:53
#: 0aaa6765f3884cda873d826d09b480a4
msgid "样本播放，适合短音效和低延迟播放"
msgstr "Sample playback, suitable for short sound effects and low-latency playback."

#: ../../source/user_guide/audio_resources.rst:54
#: e0d51a353f9248869930c8652fb04f73
msgid "``MODE_LOOP``"
msgstr "``MODE_LOOP``"

#: ../../source/user_guide/audio_resources.rst:55
#: b6b9fe2732ed4bc4b13e49d7c70dcac6
msgid "循环播放"
msgstr "Loops playback."

#: ../../source/user_guide/audio_resources.rst:56
#: fb80a37cba1b44ed9e3e6952ff71a9bb
msgid "``MODE_LOOP_BIDI``"
msgstr "``MODE_LOOP_BIDI``"

#: ../../source/user_guide/audio_resources.rst:57
#: 7e8b9e6da55d453dae94b1d27751b464
msgid "双向循环，类似来回播放"
msgstr "Bidirectional looping, similar to playing back and forth."

#: ../../source/user_guide/audio_resources.rst:59
#: 29e184289861443a9a52528700ad9470
msgid "这些标志可以用 ``|`` 组合："
msgstr "These flags can be combined with ``|``:"

